~ start
A bunch of designs for monsters. They're referred to as 'Shatterlings' and are based on personality traits, or at least that's what it sounds like.
Theres more stuff of the butterfly thing over there, some knight-looking guys...and something else that's completely different.
This guy has long claw-like fingers on his right hand that extend down to his shin. His face looks like it was burnt and his body looks like rotten flesh, with patches of red. He has long flowing hair and a crazed smile.
Says here his name is "Pride", and he would challenge the protagonist to a one-on-one duel and offer to fight by their side if he lost. He looks like a magazine model got turned into nightmare fuel...I like this guy.
